<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>퓨어 클리닉 - 피부의 본질을 찾다</title>
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Cormorant+Garamond:wght@300;400;600&family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <script>
    tailwind.config = {
      theme: {
        extend: {
          colors: {
            skin: '#F5ECE9',
            silver: '#A6A6A6',
            charcoal: '#333333',
          },
          fontFamily: {
            serif: ['Cormorant Garamond', 'serif'],
            sans: ['Noto Sans KR', 'sans-serif'],
          }
        }
      }
    }
  </script>
</head>
<body class="bg-white text-charcoal font-sans font-light">

  <!-- Nav -->
  <nav class="fixed w-full z-50 px-8 py-6 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur border-b border-gray-100 flex justify-between items-center">
    <div class="text-2xl font-serif tracking-widest text-gray-800">PURE CLINIC</div>
    <div class="hidden md:flex gap-10 text-xs tracking-widest text-gray-500">
      <a href="#about" class="hover:text-black transition">브랜드 소개</a>
      <a href="#procedures" class="hover:text-black transition">시술 안내</a>
      <a href="#doctors" class="hover:text-black transition">의료진</a>
      <a href="#contact" class="hover:text-black transition">오시는 길</a>
    </div>
    <button onclick="toggleMedical()" class="border border-gray-300 px-6 py-2 text-xs hover:border-black hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition">
      예약하기
    </button>
  </nav>

  <!-- Hero -->
  <header class="h-screen relative flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
      <img src="/images/templates/skin_clinic_hero.png" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-90">
    </div>
    <div class="relative z-10 text-center space-y-6 bg-white/30 backdrop-blur-sm p-12 rounded-full animate-fade-in aspect-square flex flex-col justify-center items-center shadow-lg border border-white/50">
      <p class="text-xs tracking-[0.3em] uppercase text-gray-600">Dermatology & Esthetic</p>
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif font-light text-gray-900 leading-tight">
        Pure Beauty, <br> <span class="italic">True You.</span>
      </h1>
      <p class="text-xs md:text-sm text-gray-700 leading-relaxed max-w-xs mx-auto">
        본연의 아름다움을 찾아드리는 1:1 맞춤 솔루션. <br>
        과학적인 진단과 섬세한 터치로 시간을 되돌립니다.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>

  <!-- Procedures -->
  <section id="procedures" class="py-24 px-6 bg-skin/30">
    <div class="container mx-auto max-w-6xl">
       <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
         <div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif text-gray-800 mb-2">Signature Programs</h2>
            <p class="text-xs text-gray-500 tracking-wider">안티에이징부터 스킨케어까지</p>
         </div>
         <a href="#" class="text-xs border-b border-gray-400 pb-1 hover:text-black hover:border-black transition mb-2 md:mb-0">전체 프로그램 보기</a>
       </div>

       <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
         <!-- Item -->
         <div class="bg-white p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition duration-500 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleMedical()">
           <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden mb-6 filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-700">
             <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1570172619644-dfd03ed5d881?q=80&w=600" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
           </div>
           <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-2">Laser Lifting</h3>
           <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
             울쎄라, 써마지 등 프리미엄 리프팅 장비를 활용하여 
             피부 탄력을 회복하고 얼굴 라인을 정리합니다.
           </p>
           <div class="text-right text-xs font-bold border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">상담 문의</div>
         </div>
         <!-- Item -->
         <div class="bg-white p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition duration-500 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleMedical()">
           <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden mb-6 filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-700">
             <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1616394584738-fc6e612e71b9?q=80&w=600" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
           </div>
           <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-2">Skin Booster</h3>
           <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
             리쥬란, 엑소좀 등 피부 재생에 탁월한 성분을 
             직접 주입하여 속건조를 해결하고 광채를 부여합니다.
           </p>
           <div class="text-right text-xs font-bold border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">상담 문의</div>
         </div>
         <!-- Item -->
         <div class="bg-white p-8 hover:shadow-xl transition duration-500 group cursor-pointer" onclick="toggleMedical()">
           <div class="h-64 overflow-hidden mb-6 filter grayscale group-hover:grayscale-0 transition duration-700">
             <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512290923902-8a9f81dc236c?q=80&w=600" class="w-full h-full object-cover">
           </div>
           <h3 class="text-xl font-serif mb-2">Whitening Care</h3>
           <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 leading-relaxed mb-4">
             기미, 잡티, 색소 침착을 개선하여 
             맑고 투명한 피부 톤으로 되돌려 드립니다.
           </p>
           <div class="text-right text-xs font-bold border-t border-gray-100 pt-4">상담 문의</div>
         </div>
       </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Doctors -->
  <section id="doctors" class="py-24 px-6 container mx-auto text-center">
    <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto space-y-6">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif">Medical Team</h2>
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-loose">
        피부과 전문의들로 구성된 퓨어 클리닉의 의료진은 
        끊임없는 연구와 풍부한 임상 경험을 바탕으로 
        안전하고 효과적인 시술을 약속드립니다.
      </p>
      <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1622253692010-333f2da6031d?q=80&w=1200" class="w-full h-64 object-cover mt-12 grayscale opacity-80">
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Modal -->
  <div id="medical-modal" class="fixed inset-0 bg-white/80 backdrop-blur-md z-[60] hidden flex items-center justify-center p-4">
    <div class="bg-white w-full max-w-md p-10 border border-gray-200 relative shadow-2xl">
      <button onclick="toggleMedical()" class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-gray-400 hover:text-black text-xl">&times;</button>
      
      <div class="text-center mb-10">
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-gray-800">Online Reservation</h2>
        <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-2">편안한 진료를 위해 예약제로 운영됩니다</p>
      </div>

      <form class="space-y-6" onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('예약 신청 완료. 확인 전화를 드리겠습니다.'); toggleMedical();">
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-xs text-gray-400">Name</label>
          <input type="text" class="w-full border-b border-gray-200 py-2 outline-none focus:border-black transition">
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-xs text-gray-400">Phone</label>
          <input type="tel" class="w-full border-b border-gray-200 py-2 outline-none focus:border-black transition">
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-xs text-gray-400">Visit Date</label>
          <input type="date" class="w-full border-b border-gray-200 py-2 outline-none focus:border-black transition text-gray-600">
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-1">
          <label class="text-xs text-gray-400">Interested In</label>
          <select class="w-full border-b border-gray-200 py-2 outline-none focus:border-black transition bg-transparent text-gray-600">
            <option>레이저 리프팅</option>
            <option>스킨 부스터</option>
            <option>색소/미백</option>
            <option>여드름/흉터</option>
            <option>기타 상담</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        
        <button class="w-full bg-charcoal text-white py-4 text-xs tracking-widest hover:bg-black transition mt-4">
          예약 신청하기
        </button>
      </form>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    function toggleMedical() {
      const modal = document.getElementById('medical-modal');
      if(modal.classList.contains('hidden')) {
        modal.classList.remove('hidden');
      } else {
        modal.classList.add('hidden');
      }
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
